# Local Worker env for exercising the lead form (pnpm dev:full).
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) on sites with lead capture. The Turnstile
# secret below is Cloudflare's ALWAYS-PASSES test key — safe for local/QA only,
# never production (production secret is set via `wrangler secret put`).
#
# Email is NOT sent in local dev (no real binding) — full delivery is verified
# only against the deployed site (see stages/ship.md). Local dev exercises the
# honeypot, Turnstile, validation, and the redirect-to-/thanks flow.
LEAD_TO="you@example.com"
LEAD_FROM="hello@example.com"
LEAD_SUBJECT="New enquiry from your website"
# LEAD_PAGE="/contact"   # only if the form lives on a standalone page (default: /#contact)
TURNSTILE_SECRET="1x0000000000000000000000000000000AA"
